189
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,560
Easy.

190
00:09:05,760 --> 00:09:06,560
Alright, young man.

191
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:07,600
This is all yours.

192
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:09,040
It's so good.

193
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:11,480
