274
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:55,920
You can just call her.

275
00:12:56,280 --> 00:12:56,760
Call her.

276
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:58,200
I did,

277
00:12:58,200 --> 00:13:00,080
